text: The Australidelphia is a superorder of Australasian marsupial mammals. It consists in five extant (living) orders, which contain most of the world's marsupials. *Superorder Australodelphia **Order Microbiotheria **Order Dasyuromorphia **Order Peramelemorphia **Order Notoryctemorphia **Order Diprotodontia **Order Yalkaparidontia (extinct) Category:Marsupials of Australia
title: Australidelphia
